===================
Running Application
===================
$LGLDIR should be defined as per README in our main directory
1.upload base station node with 'rootNode' application
2.upload a number of nodes with 'camNode' application (use different IDs)
3.run serialforwarder on your PC (e.g. on COM1: '$TOSROOT/support/sdk/c/sf/sf 9002 /dev/ttyS0 115200')
4.in 'c/' directory, run 'get_jpg 9002 1' to get bw jpg image from mote #1

=======================
buidling get_jpg.c file
=======================
1.make sure that you built /opt/tinyos-2.x/support/sdk/c/sf (libmote.a file)
  note: copy Makefile.am from $LGLDIR/support/sdk/c/sf to $TOSROOT/support/sdk/s/sf
        and enter './configure' and 'make install' to build and install libmote.a
2.we also need jpeg-6b library installed (libjpeg.a file)
3.build get_jpg.c file by typing 'make' in c/ directory